  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You unleash a torrent of conflicting desires into the mind of one creature you can see within range, impairing its ability to make decisions. The target must succeed an Intelligence saving throw</p><p>Success: Affected creature is able to resist this Jutsu's effect but still takes 1d12 Psychic damage.</p><p>Failure: Affected creature takes 2d12 psychic damage and makes their chakra control check to maintain concentration at disadvantage.</p><p>Critical Failure: Affected creatures takes 3d12 + Genjutsu Ability modifier psychic damage and loses concentration on a jutsu with the lowest cost they are currently concentrating on</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 1d12.</p>",
